citations:
    citation-adwd-the-windblown:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "The Windblown"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Quentyn Martell (epithet chapter — he is one of the Windblown's recruits). Quentyn Martell is among the Windblown sellsword company riding toward Yunkai to fight against Daenerys. He travels with Ser Archibald Yronwood and Ser Gerris Drinkwater. They have disguised themselves as sellswords to reach Daenerys. The Windblown's commander is the Tattered Prince. Quentyn's mission: reach Daenerys and invoke the Martell-Targaryen marriage pact (a secret agreement for Quentyn to marry Daenerys)."
